{
  "system_instruction": {
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "You are an intelligent AI agent in the IDEATION phase. Your role is to:\n\n1. **Understand** the user's request deeply\n2. **Brainstorm** multiple approaches to solve it\n3. **Identify** what information you need to gather\n4. **Request context searches** if you need more information\n\n## Available Capabilities:\n\n### Tools:\n{{#each available_tools}}\n- {{name}}: {{description}}\n{{/each}}\n\n### Workflows:\n{{#each workflows}}\n- {{name}}: {{description}}\n{{/each}}\n\n### Knowledge Bases:\n{{#each knowledge_bases}}\n- {{name}}: {{description}}\n{{/each}}\n\n### Recent Memories:\n{{#if memories}}\n{{#each memories}}\n- {{this}}\n{{/each}}\n{{else}}\nNo relevant memories available.\n{{/if}}\n\n### Context Search Results (if any):\n{{#if context_search_results}}\n{{#each context_search_results}}\n- {{this}}\n{{/each}}\n{{else}}\nNo context search results yet.\n{{/if}}\n\n## Current Iteration: {{iteration}} of {{max_iterations}}\n{{#if is_final_iteration}}\nThis is your FINAL iteration - you must provide a complete plan.\n{{/if}}\n\n{{#if current_plan}}\n## Previous Plan:\n- Message: {{current_plan.message}}\n- Analysis: {{current_plan.analysis.understanding}}\n- Approach: {{current_plan.analysis.approach}}\n{{/if}}\n\n## Guidelines:\n- Consider 2-4 different approaches (fewer if request is simple)\n- Identify gaps in your knowledge that need context searches\n- Be specific about what resources each approach needs\n- If you need more information, set needs_more_iteration=true and provide a context_search_request\n- Context searches can look for:\n  - Specific procedures from memories\n  - Relevant knowledge base articles\n  - Past conversation context\n  - Dynamic context about current state\n\n## Context Engine Usage:\nIf you need to search for information, provide a natural language query in context_search_request.\nExamples:\n- \"Find previous implementations of user authentication\"\n- \"Search for API documentation about payment processing\"\n- \"Look for past errors related to database connections\"\n- \"Find the current system configuration settings\""
        }
      ]
   },
  "contents": [
    {{#each conversation_history}}
    {
      "role": "{{this.role}}",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "{{json_string this.content}}"
        }
      ]
    }{{#unless @last}},{{/unless}}
    {{/each}}
  ],
  "generationConfig": {
    "responseMimeType": "application/json",
    "responseSchema": {
      "type": "OBJECT",
      "properties": {
        "iteration_notes": {
          "type": "STRING",
          "description": "Your thoughts on this iteration and what you've learned"
        },
        "needs_more_iteration": {
          "type": "BOOLEAN",
          "description": "Whether you need another iteration to gather more information"
        },
        "context_search_request": {
          "type": "STRING",
          "description": "Natural language query for the context engine if you need more information",
          "nullable": true
        },
        "execution_plan": {
          "type": "OBJECT",
          "properties": {
            "message": {
              "type": "STRING",
              "description": "Summary of your understanding and planned approach"
            },
            "analysis": {
              "type": "OBJECT",
              "properties": {
                "understanding": {
                  "type": "STRING",
                  "description": "What you understand the user wants to achieve"
                },
                "challenge": {
                  "type": "STRING",
                  "description": "Main challenges or complexities identified"
                },
                "approach": {
                  "type": "STRING",
                  "description": "Your chosen approach and why"
                }
              },
              "required": ["understanding", "challenge", "approach"]
            },
            "task": {
              "type": "ARRAY",
              "items": {
                "type": "OBJECT",
                "properties": {
                  "id": {
                    "type": "STRING",
                    "description": "Unique task identifier (e.g., task_1, task_2)"
                  },
                  "objective": {
                    "type": "STRING",
                    "description": "What this task aims to accomplish"
                  },
                  "requirements": {
                    "type": "OBJECT",
                    "properties": {
                      "requirement": {
                        "type": "ARRAY",
                        "items": {
                          "type": "STRING"
                        },
                        "description": "What is needed to complete this task"
                      }
                    },
                    "required": ["requirement"]
                  },
                  "expected_output": {
                    "type": "STRING",
                    "description": "What output or result is expected"
                  },
                  "dependencies": {
                    "type": "OBJECT",
                    "properties": {
                      "dependency": {
                        "type": "ARRAY",
                        "items": {
                          "type": "STRING"
                        },
                        "description": "Task IDs this depends on"
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  "priority": {
                    "type": "STRING",
                    "enum": ["high", "medium", "low"],
                    "description": "Task priority"
                  },
                  "failure_strategy": {
                    "type": "STRING",
                    "description": "What to do if this task fails"
                  }
                },
                "required": ["id", "objective", "requirements", "expected_output", "priority", "failure_strategy"]
              }
            },
            "success_criteria": {
              "type": "STRING",
              "description": "How to determine if the overall plan succeeded"
            }
          },
          "required": ["message", "analysis", "task", "success_criteria"]
        }
      },
      "required": ["iteration_notes", "needs_more_iteration", "execution_plan"]
    },
    "temperature": 0.8,
    "maxOutputTokens": 8192
  }
}
